tasks)\n701: - **Phase 5 (Documentation and Examples)**: Tasks 024-025 (2 tasks)\n702: - **Phase 6 (Code Quality and Finalization)**: Tasks 026-029 (4 tasks)\n703: \n704: ## Dependencies\n705: \n706: - Tasks in Phase 1 are sequential (001 → 002 → ... → 008)\n707: - Phase 2 depends on Phase 1 completion\n708: - Phase 3 depends on Phase 2 completion\n709: - Phase 4 depends on Phase 3 completion\n710: - Phase 5 can be done in parallel with Phase 4\n711: - Phase 6 depends on all previous phases\n712: \n713: ## Exit Criteria\n714: \n715: AR-001 is considered complete when:\n716: 1. All 29 tasks are marked as complete\n717: 2. All tests pass with >80% code coverage\n718: 3. CRD YAML is generated and valid\n719: 4. client-go code is generated and working\n720: 5. Documentation is updated\n721: 6. Code passes all linters\n722: 7. Generated code is up-to-date\n\n(End of file - total 722 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-001 Task Checklist: CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义\n\n## Status\nStage: ST-3 (Design) - Completed  \nPhase: ST-4 (Implementation) - In Progress\n\n---\n\n## Phase 1: Type Definition\n### [ ] TASK-001: Create package directory structure\n**Description**: Create `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` directory structure for CRD type definitions.\n\n**Verification**:\n```bash\ntest -d pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1 && echo \"Directory exists\" || echo \"Directory missing\"\n```\n\n**Acceptance Criteria**:\n- Directory `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` exists\n- Directory is writable and follows Go package conventions","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/deployment/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775840295807,"end":1775840295825}}}}
