{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775840301845,"sessionID":"ses_287abc318ffel7tpmE2F2RUOxc","part":{"id":"prt_d7854903c00103Od23iISE83XB","messageID":"msg_d78547bc30018yWgdUvVbYTFK5","sessionID":"ses_287abc318ffel7tpmE2F2RUOxc","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-5403e5e75d7843fb8482a90f8d314f9e","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-002/spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-002/spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义 Specification\n2: \n3: ## Purpose\n4: [To be filled during spec definition]\n5: \n6: ## Requirements\n7: [To be filled during spec definition]\n\n(End of file - total 7 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义 Specification\n\n## Purpose\n[To be filled during spec definition]\n\n## Requirements\n[To be filled during spec definition]","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-002/spec.md","time":{"start":1775840301826,"end":1775840301844}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775840301850,"sessionID":"ses_287abc318ffel7tpmE2F2RUOxc","part":{"id":"prt_d785492e8001Bqtu8aAXS5xOIk","messageID":"msg_d78547bc30018yWgdUvVbYTFK5","sessionID":"ses_287abc318ffel7tpmE2F2RUOxc","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-3be575c6931948d886269d37aeb63756","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-002/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-002/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # CodeInterpreter CRD Type Definition Design\n2: \n3: ## AR-002 — CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义\n4: \n5: **Module**: `pkg/apis`  \n6: **Language**: Go  \n7: **Size**: S  \n8: **Purpose**: Define Kubernetes CRD type definitions for CodeInterpreter resources, enable client-go code generation, and provide type-safe API access for code execution environment management.\n9: \n10: ## Architecture\n11: \n12: ### Package Structure\n13: \n14: ```\n15: pkg/apis/\n16: └── runtime/\n17:     └── v1alpha1/\n18:         ├── types.go                   # Core type definitions (AgentRuntime + Sandbox types)\n19:         ├── register.go                # Scheme registration\n20:         ├── doc.go                     # Package documentation\n21:         ├── deepcopy.go                # DeepCopy methods (generated)\n22:         └── types_test.go              # Unit tests\n23: ```\n24: \n25: ### API Group\n26: \n27: - **Group**: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`\n28: - **Version**: `v1alpha1`\n29: - **Scope**: `Namespaced`\n30: - **Kind**: `CodeInterpreter`\n31: - **Resource Plural**: `codeinterpreters`\n32: - **Short Names**: `ci`\n33: \n34: ### Component Interactions\n35: \n36: ```\n37: ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n38: │                     Kubernetes API Server                   │\n39: │                                                             │\n40: │  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │\n41: │  │       runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1          │  │\n42: │  │  ┌────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │  │\n43: │  │  │  codeinterpreters.runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh │  │  │\n44: │  │  └────────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │  │\n45: │  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │\n46: └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n47:                            │\n48:                            │ k8s client-go\n49:                            ▼\n50: ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n51: │                  client-go (Generated)                     │\n52: │  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │\n53: │  │  clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/         │  │\n54: │  │    • CodeInterpreterInterface                        │  │\n55: │  │    • REST CRUD + Watch                               │  │\n56: │  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │\n57: │  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │\n58: │  │  informers/externalversions/runtime/v1alpha1/        │  │\n59: │  │    • CodeInterpreterInformer                         │  │\n60: │  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │\n61: │  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │\n62: │  │  listers/runtime/v1alpha1/                          │  │\n63: │  │    • CodeInterpreterLister                           │  │\n64: │  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │\n65: └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n66:                            │\n67:                            │ Controllers\n68:                            ▼\n69: ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n70: │                   Code Execution Components                 │\n71: │  ┌─────────────────┐  ┌─────────────────┐  ┌─────────────┐ │\n72: │  │  PicoD Daemon   │  │  Session Store  │  │  Router     │ │\n73: │  │  (per pod)      │  │  (Redis)        │  │  (Nginx)    │ │\n74: │  └─────────────────┘  └─────────────────┘  └─────────────┘ │\n75: └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n76: ```\n77: \n78: ## Data Structures\n79: \n80: ### CodeInterpreter\n81: \n82: **File**: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go`\n83: \n84: ```go\n85: // +genclient\n86: // +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n87: // +k8s:openapi-gen=true\n88: // +kubebuilder:resource:shortName=ci;codeinterpreter\n89: // +kubebuilder:subresource:status\n90: // +kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Ready\",type=\"boolean\",JSONPath=\".status.ready\"\n91: // +kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Runtime\",type=\"string\",JSONPath=\".spec.runtime\"\n92: // +kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"\n93: \n94: // CodeInterpreter defines a custom resource for managing code execution environments.\n95: // It represents a code interpreter sandbox that executes user code in a secure environment.\n96: type CodeInterpreter struct {\n97:     metav1.TypeMeta   `json:\",inline\"`\n98:     metav1.ObjectMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n99: \n100:     Spec   CodeInterpreterSpec   `json:\"spec,omitempty\"`\n101:     Status CodeInterpreterStatus `json:\"status,omitempty\"`\n102: }\n103: \n104: // CodeInterpreterSpec defines the desired state of a CodeInterpreter.\n105: type CodeInterpreterSpec struct {\n106:     // Image is the container image for the interpreter (e.g., \"python:3.11-slim\").\n107:     // +required\n108:     Image string `json:\"image\"`\n109: \n110:     // Runtime specifies the execution environment type.\n111:     // +kubebuilder:default=\"python\"\n112:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Enum=python;javascript;typescript;go\n113:     // +optional\n114:     Runtime string `json:\"runtime,omitempty\"`\n115: \n116:     // Timeout defines the maximum execution time for code snippets.\n117:     // +kubebuilder:default=\"5m\"\n118:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Type=string\n119:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Format=duration\n120:     // +optional\n121:     Timeout *metav1.Duration `json:\"timeout,omitempty\"`\n122: \n123:     // Resources defines compute resource requirements for the interpreter container.\n124:     // +optional\n125:     Resources *SandboxContainerResources `json:\"resources,omitempty\"`\n126: \n127:     // Env defines environment variables to inject into the interpreter container.\n128:     // +optional\n129:     Env []SandboxEnvVar `json:\"env,omitempty\"`\n130: \n131:     // EnabledPackages specifies allowed packages for the interpreter.\n132:     // Only packages listed here can be imported/required. Empty list allows all.\n133:     // +optional\n134:     EnabledPackages []string `json:\"enabledPackages,omitempty\"`\n135: }\n136: \n137: // CodeInterpreterStatus defines the observed state of a CodeInterpreter.\n138: type CodeInterpreterStatus struct {\n139:     // Ready indicates whether the interpreter is ready to execute code.\n140:     // +optional\n141:     Ready bool `json:\"ready,omitempty\"`\n142: \n143:     // Conditions represent the latest available observations of the CodeInterpreter's current state.\n144:     // +optional\n145:     Conditions []metav1.Condition `json:\"conditions,omitempty\"`\n146: \n147:     // ObservedGeneration is the most recent generation observed by the controller.\n148:     // +optional\n149:     ObservedGeneration int64 `json:\"observedGeneration,omitempty\"`\n150: }\n151: \n152: // +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n153: \n154: // CodeInterpreterList contains a list of CodeInterpreter objects.\n155: type CodeInterpreterList struct {\n156:     metav1.TypeMeta `json:\",inline\"`\n157:     metav1.ListMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n158: \n159:     Items []CodeInterpreter `json:\"i