d `Env` reference existing Sandbox types correctly\n- JSON tags use camelCase with `omitempty` for optional fields\n\n---\n\n### [ ] TASK-002: Define CodeInterpreterStatus\n**Description**: Create `CodeInterpreterStatus` struct with ready, conditions, and observedGeneration fields.\n\n**Implementation File**: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go`\n\n**Requirements**:\n- `Ready bool` - optional field, indicates whether interpreter is ready\n- `Conditions []metav1.Condition` - optional field, latest observations of state\n- `ObservedGeneration int64` - optional field, most recent generation observed by controller\n- Follows Kubernetes status conventions\n\n**Verification**:\n```bash\ngo test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/ -run TestCodeInterpreterStatus\n```\n\n**Acceptance Criteria**:\n- `CodeInterpreterStatus` struct compiles without errors\n- `Conditions` field uses standard Kubernetes `metav1.Condition` type\n- JSON tags use camelCase with `omitempty` for optional fields\n- Status fields are optional as per Kubernetes conventions\n\n---\n\n### [ ] TASK-003: Define CodeInterpreter main type\n**Description**: Create `CodeInterpreter` struct with TypeMeta, ObjectMeta, Spec, and Status.\n\n**Implementation File**: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go`\n\n**Requirements**:\n- Embeds `metav1.TypeMeta` and `metav1.ObjectMeta`\n- Contains `Spec CodeInterpreterSpec` and `Status CodeInterpreterStatus`\n- Kubebuilder markers:\n  - `+genclient`\n  - `+genclient:nonNamespaced` (if non-namespaced, remove if namespaced is intended)\n  - `+k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object`\n  - `+k8s:openapi-gen=true`\n  - `+kubebuilder:resource:shortName=ci;codeinterpreter`\n  - `+kubebuilder:subresource:status`\n  - `+kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Ready\",type=\"boolean\",JSONPath=\".status.ready\"`\n  - `+kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Runtime\",type=\"string\",JSONPath=\".spec.runtime\"`\n  - `+kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"`\n\n**Verification**:\n```bash\ngo test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/ -run TestCodeInterpreter\n```\n\n**Acceptance Criteria**:\n- `CodeInterpreter` struct compiles without errors\n- All kubebuilder markers are present and correct\n- ShortNames \"ci\" and \"codeinterpreter\" are configured\n- Print columns for Ready, Runtime, and Age are configured\n- Status subresource is enabled\n\n---\n\n### [ ] TASK-004: Define CodeInterpreterList type\n**Description**: Create `CodeInterpreterList` struct for collection operations.\n\n**Implementation File**: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go`\n\n**Requirements**:\n- Embeds `metav1.TypeMeta` and `metav1.ListMeta`\n- Contains `Items []CodeInterpreter`\n- Has `+k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object` marker\n\n**Verification**:\n```bash\ngo test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/ -run TestCodeInterpreterList\n```\n\n**Acceptance Criteria**:\n- `CodeInterpreterList` struct compiles without errors\n- `Items` field is properly typed as `[]CodeInterpreter`\n- DeepCopy interface marker is present\n- Implements `runtime.Object` interface\n\n---\n\n### [ ] TASK-005: Verify shared types are available\n**Description**: Verify that SandboxContainerResources and SandboxEnvVar types are available for reuse.\n\n**Implementation**: Verify existing types in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go`\n\n**Requirements**:\n- `SandboxContainerResources` struct exists\n- `SandboxResourceList` struct exists\n- `SandboxEnvVar` struct exists\n- `SandboxEnvVarSource` struct exists\n- All required nested types for environment variables exist\n\n**Verification**:\n```bash\ngrep -q \"type SandboxContainerResources struct\" pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go\ngrep -q \"type SandboxEnvVar struct\" pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go\n```\n\n**Acceptance Criteria**:\n- All shared Sandbox types exist and compile\n- Types have the correct field definitions\n- Types have proper JSON tags\n\n---\n\n## Phase 2: Scheme Registr