als\n- No shared references between original and copy\n- Nested structs are properly deep copied\n\n---\n\n### [ ] TASK-011: Generate CRD YAML manifests\n**Description**: Run controller-gen to generate CRD YAML files including CodeInterpreter.\n\n**Command**:\n```bash\ncontroller-gen crd paths=\"./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/...\" output:crd:dir=manifests/charts/base/crds\n```\n\n**Verification**:\n```bash\ntest -f manifests/charts/base/crds/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_codeinterpreters.yaml && echo \"CodeInterpreter CRD generated\" || echo \"Generation failed\"\n```\n\n**Acceptance Criteria**:\n- CRD file exists at `manifests/charts/base/crds/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_codeinterpreters.yaml`\n- API group is `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`\n- Kind is `CodeInterpreter`\n- ShortNames include `ci` and `codeinterpreter`\n- Scope is `Namespaced`\n- OpenAPI v3 schema is complete\n- Default values for Runtime and Timeout are configured\n- Validation rules (enum for Runtime, duration format for Timeout) are present\n- Required fields (Image) are marked as required\n- Print columns for Ready, Runtime, and Age are configured\n\n---\n\n### [ ] TASK-012: Validate CRD YAML with dry-run\n**Description**: Apply CodeInterpreter CRD with dry-run to validate schema and structure.\n\n**Command**:\n```bash\nkubectl apply --dry-run=client -f manifests/charts/base/crds/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_codeinterpreters.yaml\n```\n\n**Verification**:\n```bash\nkubectl apply --dry-run=client -f manifests/charts/base/crds/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_codeinterpreters.yaml\n```\n\n**Acceptance Criteria**:\n- kubectl dry-run succeeds without errors\n- CRD schema is valid\n- No validation errors in the manifest\n- All required fields are present in schema\n- Default values are correctly configured\n\n---\n\n### [ ] TASK-013: Generate client-go code\n**Description**: Run code-generator to produce typed clients, informers, and listers for CodeInterpreter.\n\n**Command**:\n```bash\nbash hack/u